Package uk.ac.manchester.spinnaker.machine.datalinks

package uk.ac.manchester.spinnaker.machine.datalinks
Describes a data link. Data links connect a SpiNNaker board to something that isn't on that board, and where the messages aren't routed via Ethernet packets.
